nodes.id: 海关总署驻上海特派员办事处

zh-cn: 海关总署驻上海特派员办事处

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国海关总署设立在上海市的派出机构，直属海关总署领导，行政级别为正司局级。其主要职责为负责管辖区域内直属海关的执法督查、干部考察、廉政督察等工作。
description.en: A dispatched agency of the General Administration of Customs of the People's Republic of China established in Shanghai, directly under the leadership of the General Administration of Customs, with an administrative level of Director-General. Its main responsibilities include law enforcement supervision, cadre assessment, and integrity inspection of the customs offices under its jurisdiction.

nodes.id: 中华人民共和国海关总署

zh-cn: 中华人民共和国海关总署

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国国务院下属的正部级直属机构，统一管理全国海关。
description.en: A ministry-level agency directly under the State Council of the People's Republic of China, responsible for the unified administration of customs nationwide.

zh-cn: 上海海关高等专科学校

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国海关总署唯一直属的全日制高等院校，业务上受海关总署驻上海特派员办事处督察。
